---
title: Sweet Potato Cottage Pie with Roasted Broccoli
description: Mimi's mum is said to make the absolute best cottage pie in the world. So, Mimi whipped up this recipe for her mum, with a bit of a twist, using sweet potato in the mash! This little trick adds more fibre, vitamins and delicious flavour to the mash. Thankfully Mrs Morley gave her seal of approval (with a lot of mmmmmms to go with it)!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-potato-cottage-pie-wk6-2c08e586.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/sweet-potato-cottage-pie-wk6-33bfb665.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/sweet-potato-cottage-pie-wk6-58502dd49f236a1e622d4732
time required: 45m
nutrition:
  calories: 520 kcal
  fat: 14 g
  saturated fat: 6 g
  carbohydrates: 56 g
